                <ul>
                  <li>If you’re interested our <a class="strong" href="./services.html">services</a>, and if Nightshade’s <a class="strong" href="/values">values</a> and <a class="strong" href="/mainfesto">mission</a> resonate with you, do us all a favor and reach out! Send us an e-mail, give us a call, shoot us a text, or send out a carrier pigeon.</li>
