                  <li>Regardless of what maintenance route you opt for, Nightshade will provide on-going support for your project. Whether that be through monthly routine fertilizing, weeding, and mulching, or simply responding to a quick question you’ve got about your landscape, we’ll make ourselves available to ensure you’re fully satisfied.</li>
